 <span data-ttu-id="0dcfa-103"><xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.StopStoryboard> afeta somente uma <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard> quando ele estiver ativo (depois que o <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard> é iniciado).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0dcfa-103"><xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.StopStoryboard> only affects a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard> when it is active (after the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard> starts).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0dcfa-104">Interrompendo um gatilhos de storyboard a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline.CurrentGlobalSpeedInvalidated> e <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline.CurrentStateInvalidated> eventos, mas não o <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline.Completed> evento.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0dcfa-104">Stopping a storyboard triggers the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline.CurrentGlobalSpeedInvalidated> and <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline.CurrentStateInvalidated> events, but not the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline.Completed> event.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="0dcfa-105"><xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.PauseStoryboard> não faz referência a um <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard> diretamente.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0dcfa-105"><xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.PauseStoryboard> does not reference a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard> directly.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0dcfa-106">Em vez disso, <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.PauseStoryboard> deve fazer referência a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Name%2A> do <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard> que controla o <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0dcfa-106">Rather, <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.PauseStoryboard> must reference the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Name%2A> of the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard> that controls the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0dcfa-107">Consulte [como: usar gatilhos de eventos para controlar um Storyboard após iniciar](~/docs/framework/wpf/graphics-multimedia/how-to-use-event-triggers-to-control-a-storyboard-after-it-starts.md) para obter um exemplo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0dcfa-107">See [How to: Use Event Triggers to Control a Storyboard After It Starts](~/docs/framework/wpf/graphics-multimedia/how-to-use-event-triggers-to-control-a-storyboard-after-it-starts.md) for an example.</span></span>  
  
